### Tennis League API — Manual Test Requests
### Usage: fill in @baseUrl, @leagueId, @hostToken, @playerId, @teamId, @matchId
###        before sending requests that depend on them.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy values from the response of "Create League"
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
@leagueId  = <paste league_id here>
@hostToken = <paste host_token here>
@playerId  = <paste player_id here>
@teamId    = <paste team_id here>
@matchId   = <paste match_id here>


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════
###  League — Public Endpoints
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### Create League (minimal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/leagues
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Summer Open 2026"
}

###

### Search leagues by title prefix (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/leagues?title_prefix=sum&limit=50

###

### Create League (with description)
POST {{baseUrl}}/leagues
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Autumn Cup",
  "description": "Annual autumn tournament"
}

###

### Submit Match Result
POST {{baseUrl}}/leagues/{{leagueId}}/matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "team1_nicknames": ["alice", "bob"],
  "team2_nicknames": ["charlie", "diana"],
  "team1_score": "6",
  "team2_score": "3"
}

###

### Get Standings
GET {{baseUrl}}/leagues/{{leagueId}}/standings

###

### Get Match History
GET {{baseUrl}}/leagues/{{leagueId}}/matches

###

### Get Roster
GET {{baseUrl}}/leagues/{{leagueId}}/roster


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════
###  Admin Endpoints  (require X-Host-Token)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### Edit Player Nickname
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/leagues/{{leagueId}}/players/{{playerId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Host-Token: {{hostToken}}

{
  "new_nickname": "Serena"
}

###

### Edit Match Score
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/leagues/{{leagueId}}/matches/{{matchId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Host-Token: {{hostToken}}

{
  "team1_score": "7",
  "team2_score": "5"
}

###

### Delete Match
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/leagues/{{leagueId}}/matches/{{matchId}}
X-Host-Token: {{hostToken}}

###

### Delete Team  (delete its matches first)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/leagues/{{leagueId}}/teams/{{teamId}}
X-Host-Token: {{hostToken}}
